These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, bluemaster
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, may
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, chess
2 different games are played: billiard, chess
1. the person playing billiard is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##8
2. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
3. the prince-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Cigar      | bluemaster     | prince      |
| Birthday          | may | january    |
| Hobby         | chess   | board-games |
| Game   | billiard  | chess      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, alhambra
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, woodworking
City: miami, paris
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, biathlon
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to miami##5
3. the person traveling to paris is not to the right of the person traveling to miami##8
4. the person who's sport is handball is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Cigar    | cain        | alhambra    |
| Hobby       | filmmaking         | woodworking |
| City         | paris | miami   |
| Sport   | handball               | biathlon  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  scientist, pilot
There 2 different types of food: peas, artichoke
2 different pets are kept: cat, ferret
1. the person eating peas is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating artichoke is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
3. the scientist is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Sport   | biathlon       | climbing |
| Job   | scientist       | pilot    |
| Food   | peas | artichoke |
| Pet           | cat        | ferret   |

