The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, nurse
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, rose
House: victorian, futuristic
1. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5
2. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the left of the futuristic house##8
3. the futuristic house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Birthday         | april | march  |
| Job           | nurse  | designer |
| Flower   | rose | begonia   |
| House     | futuristic   | victorian |

