2. the person who likes lavender is not to the right of the french##8
3. the french is on the right of the japanese##1
4. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Birthday   | february | may |
| Nationality   | japanese    | french     |
| Color         | lavender  | red    |
| Beverage     | mirinda     | tea       |

