2. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person eating plum##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |
| Food          | plum         | corn    |
| Movie-Genre           | animation | disaster   |
| House   | cottage   | modern    |
| Music-Genre     | metal         | salsa |

 